&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a Director, Brand Design who can bridge product and marketing — a hybrid thinker who crafts beautiful, scalable systems and brings them to life in campaigns, UI, and content. You’ll sit in the Growth org, led by Morgan Brown, and partner closely with Product Design, Creative, and Comms. Your north star: make every experience — from ad to app — feel unmistakably Opendoor, and use a refreshed design system as a growth lever.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a player-coach role: you’ll set the vision, build the system and standards, ship real work, and mentor your team and collaborators across functions.&lt;/p&gt;
