&lt;h1&gt;Why Now&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Seller growth is critical to Opendoor&#39;s success. Every seller who starts on our website represents helping a new homeowner achieve their goals and we know our funnel can be significantly improved. We&#39;re looking for a Growth PM to own the full seller journey from first click to request submission, optimizing our website, landing pages, and onboarding flows to drive measurable lift in acquisition and activation. This is a high-impact, high-visibility role where your experiments will directly move company-level metrics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;The Role&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a Growth Product Manager who will own seller growth end-to-end; from opportunity sizing through experimentation to shipped product. You&#39;ll partner closely with Growth Engineering, Data Science, Design, and Marketing to identify high-leverage improvements, run rigorous A/B tests, and scale what works, driving measurable improvements in seller acquisition and activation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a hands-on, technical role. You&#39;ll write SQL to size opportunities, analyze experiment results, and dig into funnel data. You won&#39;t wait for analysts to get back to you, you&#39;ll find the answers yourself and move fast.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Funnel Optimization &amp;amp; Experimentation&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Own the seller growth funnel from website visit through request submission; identify and prioritize the highest-leverage optimization opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Design, launch, and analyze A/B tests across website, landing pages, and onboarding flows: driving measurable improvements in conversion rates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Build a rigorous experimentation roadmap; maintain velocity of experiments per sprint while ensuring statistical validity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
