&lt;p&gt;At Opendoor our goal is to build the largest, most trusted housing platform and set a new standard for how people move.&amp;nbsp; We’ve combined our deep, proprietary data and operational expertise with the power of artificial intelligence (AI) to make online home selling and buying radically simple.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re seeking an IT Platform Engineer to combine software engineering expertise with IT infrastructure domain knowledge and a passion for automation and enablement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Modernize Windows infrastructure hosting our heavily customized ResWare platform, title/escrow software requiring Office 365,&amp;nbsp; Azure AD, network file sharing, SQL, and DMZ network for full features and automations.&lt;/li&gt;
