&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a passionate and resourceful Organic Social Lead to own and elevate Opendoor&#39;s presence across all social media platforms. As our dedicated organic social expert, you will be a one-person creative engine responsible for the entire content lifecycle—from initial concept to final post. This is a foundational role with the opportunity to define our voice, build our community, and create content that turns followers into fans and fans into customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You are a true creator at heart—a storyteller who can script, shoot, and edit compelling content independently. You live and breathe social trends and understand how to translate a powerful brand mission into platform-native content that stops the scroll. This role sits within the Growth organization and is perfect for a self-starter who thrives on autonomy and is excited to make a measurable impact.&lt;/p&gt;
