&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;End-to-End Content Creation: Act as a self-contained creator: concepting, scripting, shooting, editing, and publishing a high volume of compelling content. This includes short-form video (Reels, TikToks), static graphics, carousels, and engaging stories.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
