&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Designer (Senior)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location: Toronto or Seattle&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Opendoor is on a mission to tilt the world in favor of homeowners by making buying and selling simple and fast. We&#39;re solving one of the most complex, high-stakes transactions in people&#39;s lives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a versatile Product Designer to join our lean, focused team. You&#39;ll primarily work on Growth (landing pages, top-of-funnel experiences, acquisition), but you&#39;ll also flex across our Seller and Buyer domains as priorities shift. This role is for someone who thrives in variety and can context-switch quickly without losing momentum.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll work in a fast-paced environment where priorities shift weekly, and you&#39;ll need to be comfortable owning multiple workstreams simultaneously. This is an in-person role based in Toronto.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
